text: Home-cooked taste tze-char at affordable prices! Food tasted good. Plenty of seatings. A little warm tho. Can't complain much!

Feel cheated by Feng Wei Sea Food, ordered a roasted chicken but was given chicken chop.
Store assistant fail to inform us the availability of the roasted chicken, assuming..
Instead they choose to mislead us by placing 2 pieces of chicken wing and bunch of prawn cracker to cover up the chicken chop.
Only comes to realize it was a fraud when the taste and textures was different.

As a regular that always patron them I am disappointed and would boycott them as it was not the money or the services issue. It's the integrity of the store.
Only Seafood stall that charges a $3 surcharge for vegetable dish till Day 15 of CNY. $13 for small plate of Kang Kong. Daylight robbery for those that stay nearby and lazy to venture out.

One of the best coffee shops I've been to. There were a lot of seats available when I visited, it seems to not be too crowded as its not located near any malls or shopping areas which makes it a pretty peaceful and chill place to have a meal.

The coffee shop has a tall ceiling which allows huge fans to be installed, making the place very cooling with good ventilations.
There was also a TV üì∫ installed on the pillar, allowing people to watch shows while they have their meal üôÇ

From most stalls that I've seen, the food prices were shockingly low considering the inflation lately. This place feels like a hidden gem üíé  and I'm sure most people who live around here are happy that stallowners are not increasing the prices too much and providing great food. üëç

I managed to try out both the Western food stall and Korean Japanese food stall, both of which were delicious and affordable. üëç

I had an enjoyable meal here and will definitely come back again in the future if I am nearby. üôÇüëç

27/5 I have ordered 4 dishes but yam ring based was dark brown. Called  but did not picked up my call  probably they were busy.
30/5 shown them picture and immediately their chef fried another kosong
yam ring for me the incident was happened  a few days later. .
I was impressed of their prompt service recovery..
Their curry veggie were good, Bee hoon nice but a bit oily. Overall experience was good and I will plan to order again for my next event
